title: Fischer-Z - The Very Best Fischer Z Album  Ever 2001
description:
Very Best Fischer Z Album Ever (2001)
Import only compilation from the veteran Art/Pop rockers led by vocalist, guitarist and songwriter John Watts. Fischer Z (pronounced Fischer Zed) have been described as, 'equal parts Roxy Music and Talking Heads with Art/Pop and Prog Rock leanings'. While this description is appropriate, there is somore...
